{"tid":1049163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"短裙女與男友爭執　瀡落林村河企圖自殺","createTime":"2019-03-06T05:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T11:12:16.000Z","uid":145520,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f214ab6d277db39ffab3ecd2648c22341d0f4c7","tid":1049163,"uid":145520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢係想點死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日(6日)凌晨3時許，一名身穿短裙紮馬尾26歲姓熊女子，在大埔太和邨麗和樓對開與男友因故起爭執，期間，她突然情緒激動，跑至林村河沿斜坡瀡落約3米乾涸河道企圖自殺，男友大驚報警。 <br />\n<br />\n消防蛙人到場待命，警員落河協助將赤腳手腳受傷流血女子，帶回安全位置，再送院治理，其男友則由警員帶返警署協助調查。案件列企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsvBHRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsvBHRC.png&h=5e53a241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306042537936-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190306042537936-0306_00822_001.html&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=83b9b906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306042537936-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e034e184c62067ab67b335313a220d3941567a3","tid":1049163,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"哎喲不錯哦"},{"pid":"f65d44ce67545015553d3de4ea714b40cc559c21","tid":1049163,"uid":229872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"玩咁大條仔仲點敢同佢繼續一齊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b40f38efca95bbdb34a03f8f5a70d72ea0ad5b5","tid":1049163,"uid":145520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f65d44ce67545015553d3de4ea714b40cc559c21","tid":1049163,"uid":229872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"玩咁大條仔仲點敢同佢繼續一齊呀<img sr